SCP-3787: The Horse Meme


01 Mar 2018 03:24








SCP-3787:  The Horse Meme

Author:  Lt Flops
附加记录：    
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Okay, here's my second SCP. This existed in many different iterations between May 2017 and when I posted it, and between then and now. Before I posted it, I had adapted it to fit under the Hiemal classification after I was inspired by these two articles:

AbsentmindedNihilist
DrBleep


Another inspiration here was the qntm. Given when this SCP was conceived, however, it deviates significantly from qntm's portrayal of the Division.

Per stormbreath's recommendation, this article now fits under the Archon classification.
